sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant WebApp as Web App
    participant AuthAPI as Auth API
    participant EmailSvc as Email Service
    participant AuditLog as Audit Log

    User->>WebApp: Submit email address
    WebApp->>AuthAPI: POST /password-reset
    AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: Validate request without revealing account existence
    opt Account exists
        AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: Create reset token and store only its hash
        AuthAPI->>EmailSvc: Send reset link
    end
    AuthAPI->>AuditLog: Write security event
    AuthAPI-->>WebApp: Generic success response
    User->>WebApp: Open reset link and enter new password
    WebApp->>AuthAPI: Submit new password with reset token
